response.overview: The Chicana story is complicated. Although the Census would like to lump us together under a single manufactured label, the reality is we come from many different backgrounds, different places and different cultures.  The hour-long documentary premiered at the Denver Film Festival. The screening sold out overnight, as did an advanced screening at History Colorado. The demand prompted a third and final showing of the film on the big screen thanks to Regis University.
response.title: I AM DENVER
